{
  "stem": "3165.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so now I was here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And-- and then they were saying something that the Germans might be running back now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, the Russians are-- are advancing, whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were just burning, like, the highways, the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] different factories, whatever was-- they were burning everything, whatever they could, running back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I just remember at night seeing big flames, big fires all over us, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And also during this period, a lot of diphtheria broke out on-- on this farm where I was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And three different farmers-- three people died in each-- one person died in each house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, there was no vaccination, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But luckily, it didn't hit our-- this house where I was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So nobody was touched here with diphtheria.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they treated me fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They treated me--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--as long as I was doing the work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While I was in the-- well, there was very few Jews left already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- in fact, nobody was in the open.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If-- if there were any left, they were either hiding or-- you know, they knew that no Jews already-- all the Jews are finished, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] unless they can find them where they were hiding.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of them were hiding in forests and in different places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're in '44.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're in '44.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now-- now we're in January, early January, I think, believe, '45?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we wake up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I guess they-- you know, the people knew that the Russians are-- are advancing and they're coming, and the Germans are going back.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
